{"tid":1419443,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(Idea) 818，香港最後一場和平示威","createTime":"2019-08-06T01:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T22:16:33.000Z","uid":288491,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64530950736f89b32d5e6bf15a68b55eb960a134","tid":1419443,"uid":288491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:23:02.000Z","msg":"首先，我係P牌仔，對唔住，90度躹躬先<br />\n<br />\n元朗黑社會打人，到荃灣黑社會斬人，黑警唔拉人，都見政府武力升級，愈來愈唔要臉<br />\n<br />\n不如我地和理非搞埋最後一場和平示威，如果政府再唔回應市民5大訴求，呢個將會香港最後一之和平示威。以後就算有人掟核彈都唔分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解揀8月18日？<br />\n1：818事件，好記易入腦，容易留係歷史<br />\n2: Short break 比勇武，示威者抖抖。有時間反思一下點樣再做好啲<br />\n3：多啲時間做文宣，期間努力爭取更多市民上街<br />\n4：試多次全球登報紙，話比全世界聽，而家係官逼民反<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n簡單總結一下目的：和理非對政府最後通知，再唔回應5大訴求，以後唔會再有和平示威，就算掟核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得可唔可行？"},{"pid":"8623334923147543d8084db25c6803184f136d27","tid":1419443,"uid":288491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:23:57.000Z","msg":"概念圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndvcDKg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndvcDKg.png&h=b2d69128&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67aa23bb9d317bee84a086da5011ea86fd91cf81","tid":1419443,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:24:37.000Z","msg":"18號唔係有其他遊行咩"},{"pid":"eda7fe154cbe5d094ae4f6a023526c97e8f01b06","tid":1419443,"uid":288491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:24:37.000Z","msg":"UE 得E，唔識做文宣 sor"},{"pid":"b9f74e597551bbcff14547618e6c986791831a89","tid":1419443,"uid":288491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67aa23bb9d317bee84a086da5011ea86fd91cf81","tid":1419443,"uid":92467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:24:37.000Z","msg":"18號唔係有其他遊行咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:25:00.000Z","msg":"可以其他日子既"},{"pid":"1eacedda5c162b596e5b2569d2828310fa68ce86","tid":1419443,"uid":262035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedB